    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that's a relief. i was really worried it was getting infected. how often should i be applying the antibiotic cream? and is it okay to use a bit of standard rubbing alcohol to wipe the area first to make sure it's totally sterile before the cream goes on?",
